      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized camshaft phasing. This specimen features a reinforced rear subframe and a documented rod bearing service, addressing the critical mechanical pain points of the chassis. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power through a limited-slip M-Variable Lock differential. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution remains uncompromised. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior bolsters are in showroom state, free of typical wear or UV degradation.",
